&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit Endoscopy nurses to join our enthusiastic team at Band 5.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work with the friendly multidisciplinary team in providing patient centred care for patients undergoing therapeutic GI endoscopy, bronchoscopy and cystoscopy. You will be involved in the in service training and will have the opportunity to enhance your own training and development with courses and will be involved in training others on an informal and formal basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are vacancies across all 3 sites, St George&#39;s, Tooting, Queen Mary&#39;s Hospital, Roehampton and The Nelson in Wimbledon.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Post are fixed term for 6 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
